X: 137
T: All Hail The Power Of Jesus' Name
C: Words: Edward Perronet, 1780. Music: 'Coronation' Oliver Holden, 1793.
C: Setting: SSAATTBB arr. from "The Church Hymnal, Revised and Enlarged" (Episcopal), 1896.
C: copyright: public domain.
M: 4/4
L: 1/4
Q: 1/4=120
