W:1.All hail the power of Jesus' name! Let angels prostrate fall;
W:Bring forth the royal diadem, and crown Him Lord of all.
W:Bring forth the royal diadem, and crown Him Lord of all.
W:
W:2.Crown Him, ye martyrs of our God, who from His altar call;
W:Extol the Stem of Jesse's Rod, and crown Him Lord of all.
W:Extol the Stem of Jesse's Rod, and crown Him Lord of all.
W:
W:3.Ye seed of Israel's chosen race, ye ransomed from the fall,
W:Hail Him who saves you by His grace, and crown Him Lord of all.
W:Hail Him who saves you by His grace, and crown Him Lord of all.
W:
W:4.Hail Him, ye heirs of David's line, whom David Lord did call,
W:The God incarnate, Man divine, and crown Him Lord of all,
W:The God incarnate, Man divine, and crown Him Lord of all.
